testcase.name: Scrolling to bottom of the page and Verify "show more results" button
Click on "show more results" button and validate the count of doctorList
Scroll back to top and Enter Valid Location inputfield
Select Entry from suggestions and click on search button
Check Online Bookable Checkbox and Validate the timeFrame Element is Visble
Click on Search Button and Validate physicians with online bookable appointments are displayed
Check „Video-Conference“-Checkbox, empty the "Name" inputfield and click the „Search Button“ Validate physician with Video Conference
Uncheck „Video-Conference“ Checkbox, check „Barrier-Free“ Checkbox and click search button then Validate barrier-free state are displayed
Check the „Alphabetical-Sort“ option in the sorting section and validate that data should be sorted by physician lastname
Check the „Distance-Sort“ option in the sorting section and validate sorted by relative distance
Drage the Slide bar and Release
